Description:
Each pack contains the following:-
one pair of green and one pair of white plastic knitting needles size 8 (4mm) and size 10 (3.25mm).
Cassette featuring knitting instructions and other useful information.
A ring-lock binder in which to organise your addresses and other notes.
Comes with 50 sheets of Manilla paper.
Brailon refills also available for longer lasting notes (Product no. BP25).
50 pegs: 5 each of black, ,"purplish" brown, white, blue, red, purple, green, yellow, orange and pink.
